cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with multi-modal learning for object detection using deep learning techniques. The primary focus is on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) with a secondary focus on artificial intelligence (AI), multimedia (MM), and neural networks (NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.NE.
